divs: Sighting DetailsTalking to neighbors, neighbor pointed it out, I did not know until they told me. It was 8:01 pm. First thought it was the moon, but it was different. The orb slowly move toward the north with no noise. Watched it until I'd was to far away .
Summary: Round shaped ,looked like designs on it ,slow traveling , took picture of it with I phone
